'''糯比语'''(自称: ''Lolbiq'';<ref>张佩芝. 1998. ''哈尼语哈雅方言土语词汇对照''. Kunming: 云南民族出版社.</ref> ''{{IPA|lu21 pi33}}''<ref>[http://www.doc88.com/p-97281176367.html 云南民族识别参考资料] {{Wayback|url=http://www.doc88.com/p-97281176367.html |date=20200516161059 }} (1955), p.61</ref>或[[金平苗族瑶族傣族自治县|金平苗族瑶族傣族自治县]]的''{{IPA|lo˥bi˨˩}}''，意为“下游”；<ref name="Bradley2001">Bradley, David. 2001. ''Northern Hani dialects''. Paper presented at the 34th International Conference on Sino-Tibetan Languages and Linguistics (ICSTLL 34), Kunming, China, 24-28 October 2001.</ref>汉语名“糯比”指[[云南省|云南省]]中南部一种[[彝语|彝语]]。
==分布==
糯比语分布在：
*[[新平彝族傣族自治县|新平彝族傣族自治县]] (''新平县志'' 1993:106, 118)
*[[元江哈尼族彝族傣族自治县|元江哈尼族彝族傣族自治县]] (''元江县志'' 1993:81)
*[[金平苗族瑶族傣族自治县|金平苗族瑶族傣族自治县]] (''金平县志'' 1994:113-132)

据戴庆厦(2009)所言<ref>戴庆厦. 2009. ''元江县羊街乡语言使用现状及其演变''. Beijing: 商务印书馆. {{ISBN|9787100066037}}</ref>，在[[元江哈尼族彝族傣族自治县|元江哈尼族彝族傣族自治县]]羊街乡的哈尼族属于[[糯美语|糯美语]]和糯比语次群，在乡里分别有9,000人和6,000人。[[糯美语|糯美语]]主要使用在戈垤、<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.ynszxc.gov.cn/villagePage/vIndex.aspx?departmentid=251857|title=元江县羊街乡戈垤村民委员会|website=www.ynszxc.gov.cn|access-date=18 February 2018|archive-date=2018-02-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180219031152/http://www.ynszxc.gov.cn/villagePage/vIndex.aspx?departmentid=251857|dead-url=no}}</ref>党舵<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.ynszxc.gov.cn/villagePage/vIndex.aspx?departmentid=251859 |title=存档副本 |access-date=2021-03-20 |archive-date=2018-02-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180218211930/http://www.ynszxc.gov.cn/villagePage/vIndex.aspx?departmentid=251859 |dead-url=no }}</ref>(也有[[苦聪话|苦聪话]]使用者)和坝木<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.ynszxc.gov.cn/villagePage/vIndex.aspx?departmentid=251858 |title=存档副本 |access-date=2021-03-20 |archive-date=2018-02-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180219031126/http://www.ynszxc.gov.cn/villagePage/vIndex.aspx?departmentid=251858 |dead-url=no }}</ref>几个自治乡，而糯比语主要分布在朗支<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.ynszxc.gov.cn/villagePage/vIndex.aspx?departmentid=251862|title=元江县羊街乡浪支村民委员会|website=www.ynszxc.gov.cn|access-date=18 February 2018|archive-date=2018-02-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180218211933/http://www.ynszxc.gov.cn/villagePage/vIndex.aspx?departmentid=251862|dead-url=no}}</ref>(也在中梁子有彝语使用者<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.ynszxc.gov.cn/villagePage/vIndex.aspx?departmentid=252257|title=元江县羊街乡浪支村民委员会中良子|website=www.ynszxc.gov.cn|access-date=18 February 2018|archive-date=2018-02-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180219031113/http://www.ynszxc.gov.cn/villagePage/vIndex.aspx?departmentid=252257|dead-url=no}}</ref>)、羊街<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.ynszxc.gov.cn/villagePage/vIndex.aspx?departmentid=251861|title=元江县羊街乡羊街村民委员会|website=www.ynszxc.gov.cn|access-date=18 February 2018|archive-date=2018-02-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180218210339/http://www.ynszxc.gov.cn/villagePage/vIndex.aspx?departmentid=251861|dead-url=no}}</ref>和垤霞<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.ynszxc.gov.cn/villagePage/vIndex.aspx?departmentid=251860|title=元江县羊街乡垤霞村民委员会|website=www.ynszxc.gov.cn|access-date=18 February 2018|archive-date=2018-02-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180218210232/http://www.ynszxc.gov.cn/villagePage/vIndex.aspx?departmentid=251860|dead-url=no}}</ref> (包括依垤<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.ynszxc.gov.cn/villagePage/vIndex.aspx?departmentid=252243|title=元江县羊街乡垤霞村民委员会依垤|website=www.ynszxc.gov.cn|access-date=18 February 2018|archive-date=2018-02-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180218210257/http://www.ynszxc.gov.cn/villagePage/vIndex.aspx?departmentid=252243|dead-url=no}}</ref> (Dai 2009:113))等几个村。

